AM must persuade DRAM vendors to provide precise information on their defenses, limitations, and necessary supplemental solutions.\u003c/p\u003e\n","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/6ornt1/stop_hammer_time_rethinking_our_approach","submitter_user":{"username":"kuijsten","created_at":"2018-09-06T05:56:47.000-05:00","is_admin":false,"about":"","is_moderator":false,"karma":578,"avatar_url":"/avatars/kuijsten-100.png","invited_by_user":"taal","github_username":"timkuijsten"},"tags":["hardware","pdf","security"]}]